.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, pomegranate
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, video-games
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus  |
| Hobby   | video-games | card-games |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | lizard     |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, indian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indian     |
| Pet           | pony          | lizard     |

